Positive: first time request, connections.dat file is created or extended and record of connection is added, connections.dat file not created

Negative: connection already pending from the same sender and same receiver, connections.dat file created with pending connection from current user to recipient

Edge: tests if current user has a request being sent to it, connections.dat file created with other user pending connection against current

Negative 2: user does not exist

Negative 3: already connected to user, connections.dat file created with a CONNECTED config
